        <title><![CDATA[SAFARI 2000 PRE- AND POST-FIRE REFLECTANCE NEAR KAOMA, ZAMBIA, DRY SEASON 2000]]></title>

        <onlink><![CDATA[http://daac.ornl.gov/mercury_harvest/757.xml]]></onlink>
        
